Detailed Description

Compiler specific defines.

Author:
Modtronix Engineering
Dependencies:
none
Compiler:
MPLAB C18 v2.10 or higher
HITECH PICC-18 V8.35PL3 or higher

Description

This module is an interface between the code and different compilers. It defines generic names for compiler specific defines and variables.
